This document contains a clear, practical, step-by-step guide to build a small React front-end for a jewelry shop with the following pages:

Landing (Home)

Add Product

Inventory

Billing (POS)

Stack: React (Vite), React Router, Tailwind CSS, localStorage for demo persistence.


src/
 ├── components/
 │     ├── Navbar.jsx
 ├── pages/
 │     ├── Landing.jsx
 │     ├── AddProduct.jsx
 │     ├── Inventory.jsx
 │     ├── Billing.jsx
 ├── App.js
 ├── index.js